Sesty Lettieri, Appellant, v. Rosa Stabile, Individually and as Executrix of John Lettieri, Deceased, et al., Respondents.

Motion for reargument denied, without costs. Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied.

Present — Wenzel, Acting P. J., Beldock, Murphy, Ughetta and Kleinfeld, JJ. [See ante, p. 844.]
